rk多<br />\nRouter switch個d <br />\nEg telcom公司，大公司in-house都有<br />\n<br />\nSolution <br />\n做coding多,code 狗<br />\ne.g pccw solution</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外想問下巴打 Infrastructure 唔使點打code??"},{"pid":"45fbfcc91b528f034945e49b68b2a2806ae934fe","tid":154632,"uid":76740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>PDLC model:<br />\nWaterfall, agile<br />\n<br />\nWaterfall:<br />\nPlanning<br />\nRequirement analysis<br />\nDesign development<br />\nTesting <br />\nPost implementation maintenance <br />\n<br />\nAgile:<br />\nScrum<br />\nSprint<br />\nSprint planning<br />\nGrooming/ refinement<br />\nSprint review<br />\nRetrospective <br />\nRelease</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打講到好遠 係咪講緊software design果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姐係做solution?"},{"pid":"500ea1a23357b65548883734e6679111ebd03187","tid":154632,"uid":83330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:49:00.000Z","msg":"LM"}]}